                                "stop": 9.131,
                                "byte_start": 81844,
                                "byte_stop": 118415,
                                "text": "The opinion of the court in No. 91-1618 Voinovich versus Quilter would be announced by Justice O\u0027Connor."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 9.131,
                        "stop": 197.355,
